HtmlItemData.Html:
Job Satisfaction Survey
 
 
Please complete the following survey as honestly as you can.  This information will help the company serve you better as an employee.  Thank you.

ItemTexts_MatrixItemData.TextValue: To what extent do you agree or disagree with the following statements:

MatrixCategoryTexts.TextValue: My department has a climate in which diverse perspectives are encouraged and valued
I understand the day to day objectives of my department
My department operates in a cost-efficient manner
I have access to adequate information which enables me to do my job well
I understand and am satisfied with the direction and priorities of my department
The amount of work expected of me in my job is reasonable

ItemTexts_Select1Data.TextValue: Considering all of the above, how satisfied are you in your job?

ItemTexts_MessageItemData.TextValue: Thank you for taking the survey.

ItemTexts_MultiLineTextItemData.TextValue: Please explain the reasons you are not satisfied in your job:
